      <talk_question mid="184"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Joey$<BR>Oh, adventurer. You know, that strange guy who claimed to be a pirate? I looked up about him and he really was a pirate last time!<BR>Isn't it strange? Oh my goodness… He robs in the mountains but he is a pirate!<BR>Why is a pirate in the mountain…… Hmm?!</html>]]></talk_question>
